divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting in the passenger seat of my car while my 1512 year old daughterwas driving East on Manatee Drive in Navarre Florida Near Gulf Breeze.Up in the clear almost dusk sky was a silvery rectangle shaped object hoveringin one place about 3,000 feet up in front of me. A plane passed over it andstill it remained hovering. I asked my daughters if they could see the object,they both said yes. They also described it as I saw it. The object stayed inthe sky above me for 3-4 minutes and then in an instant second it was gone. Ithought it may be a star but a star is round and not rectangular. I remainedcalm and was totally amazed by this thing. I just told this account to myhusband and he told me to report it to MUFON.
Summary: Witnessed rectangular shaped object in the sky
